Description of hubspotapi set by Hubspot
Cookie name:
hubspotapi
Purpose:
This cookie allows the user to access the app with the correct permissions. the cookie itself is short-lived (5mins), but the authorization will persist for 28 days if "remember me" is checked, or for 7 days if not checked. After that, we make the user login again.
